.</span><hr size=1> Gotta refire up this topic. My friend at work pointed this out to me, but I'll label it spoiler because these things arent readily noticable in the theatrical trailer. Again this is not a spoiler for story in Revolutions, but rather a revelation from the trailer for...Revolutions. Yeah. Anyway...<br>
